data.description: East Side living and MacArthur Schools a great combination. Great Starter Home in MacArthur Park Community. Walkways and Green areas, Community Pool. Three bedrooms, two bathrooms, with 2 car garage. Nice entry, living room with Vaulted ceilings and brick gas fireplace. Seller is leaving a wall mount in the living room. The kitchen features white cabinetry and stainless-steel appliances, and a Large Window above the sink makes it easy to see the backyard and what the kids are up to!  Dining area with doors to Covered Patio. The utility room is near off Kitchen. Nice size bedrooms and Primary suite features 2 closets and Nicely remodeled 3/4 bath. Backyard with shed. The garage has one new door. Storm cellar in garage floor.
